Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me more of that thick and incredible stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...this face of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Darling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:46.82,Alternate,,0,0,0,,T-Tarou-san has been making such a face...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:50.51,Alternate,,0,0,0,,At the moment when we saw each other's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:54.56,Alternate,,0,0,0,,This mask... This mask of mine as a wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:58.43,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I felt it breaking in pieces.
